 as an Int and \"TargetActor\" as a Float, which seems incorrect based on the OnPossess setup). You may want to fix those later.\n\nOnce you set the **AI Controller Class** in Boss_BP, your boss will automatically use the AI Controller when spawned/placed, and the behavior tree will start running!\n\nWould you like me to help you troubleshoot the blackboard key type mismatches I noticed?"},{"type":"checkpoint","info":{"id":"1f0cf974-e3e4-646c-8004-2494746ac270"}},{"type":"checkpoint","info":{"id":"1f0cf975-504c-6836-8005-37444c1c07a3"}}]}],"Mapping":{"node_agent_names":{"pairs":[{"first":"DB10892D4C0BD0C676C392874576E598","second":"ConstructionScript_0"},{"first":"72941CEC46F3B3CB116BA5A45B2AB37D","second":"EventBeginPlay_0"},{"first":"6992B01C46C3B43D279E6BA30E3F1077","second":"EventActorBeginOverlap_0"},{"first":"21D8AD2146817FF313828BA9B0F905F1","second":"EventTick_0"},{"first":"251984FF44FDD85EE0FFA68B687EE1AC","second":"ConstructionScript_1"},{"first":"6820EF72453ADBE186F98BB53A0C4F16","second":"SetValueasObject_0"},{"first":"B8834F1A46253002A7EAFFAD635B4E21","second":"EventBeginPlay_1"},{"first":"D861E14344BDC7D8D45136A4E67E07F5","second":"PrintString_0"},{"first":"57CB864E4152E04C53B55BAAD2316652","second":"EventTick_1"},{"first":"F436C5064A45CF767BCE6D9EC017B6CF","second":"RunBehaviorTree_0"},{"first":"6FC4EDA74B7B173C6FB0808367AC4CE5","second":"EventOnPossess_0"},{"first":"7FC69EBD43453FBA97F00BAFAA6374CB","second":"SetValueasInt_0"},{"first":"7A61FB834E6477DD80BA43AE42801660","second":"SetValueasFloat_0"},{"first":"98E7ACCE4E708D06D4F03A8AA308D465","second":"SetValueasObject_1"},{"first":"E4964E5948654A2FBB9AB1AD3DE7EB37","second":"SetValueasObject_2"},{"first":"78BEE8E8407896009BE5758A014D5D30","second":"GetBlackboard_0"},{"first":"7E9DE389448CDBF971231F8C7ECE7407","second":"MakeLiteralName_0"},{"first":"CE649F524C3A8F0D7EF99ABE16DA70EA","second":"MakeLiteralName_1"},{"first":"BE49D96045D833BDAA0CD89C9E065009","second":"CastToPlayer_BP_0"},{"first":"94D38